🚀 Live Now! (9/1 - 9/7) 🚀

We’re changing things up on how we do merch moving forward. In order to bring you guys the best products, the best koality goods, we are moving to a PREORDER model. All orders will ship around 3 weeks but OH TRUST ME!! It’ll be worth the wait 🐨👊🏼💪

1) Preorder - 1 week window (9/1 - 9/7)
2) New collection drops monthly
3) New garments
4) Koality products 
5) Limited editions

Pretty pumped to share with you guys what we’ve been working on! Don’t forget to tag #teamvonmoger #vonmogercrew

🛒 VonMoger.com
